videos.description: Paul George drains a 3-pointer from the wing and on the next possession, Marcus Morris gets in for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Paul George, Marcus Morris get Clippers rolling early) 2021/06/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paul George, Marcus Morris get Clippers rolling early

videos.description: Patrick Beverley intercepts a pass and then breaks away for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beverley converts steal into a bucket) 2021/06/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beverley converts steal into a bucket

videos.description: DeMarcus Cousins slams down a huge one-handed dunk over Dario Saric while drawing contact.
videos.headline: Cousins emphatically posterizes Saric

videos.description: Mikal Bridges and Deandre Ayton drop in easy buckets on back-to-back possessions.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bridges, Ayton keeping Suns in it) 2021/06/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bridges, Ayton keeping Suns in it

videos.description: Deandre Ayton coming up huge for the Suns as he dunks on back-to-back possessions.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ayton throws down back-to-back jams) 2021/06/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ayton throws down back-to-back jams

videos.description: The Suns display good passing to find Mikal Bridges in the corner for a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ball movement leads to Bridges' 3-pointer) 2021/06/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ball movement leads to Bridges' 3-pointer

videos.description: Devin Booker looks unguardable as he gets in the zone and sinks four straight buckets in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Booker drains 4 straight buckets) 2021/06/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker drains 4 straight buckets

videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets the pass from Devin Booker and charges at the rim to stuff down a dunk with emphasis to ignite the Phoenix Suns crowd.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ayton hammers down emphatic slam in the 4th quarter) 2021/06/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ayton hammers down emphatic slam in the 4th quarter

videos.description: After recording a 40-point, 11-assist, 13-rebound triple-double, Devin Booker tells Rachel Nichols that he and the Suns are focused and locked in on Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Booker laser focused after huge triple-double in Game 1 win vs. Clippers) 2021/06/20

videos.headline: Booker laser focused after huge triple-double in Game 1 win vs. Clippers
